    "text": "Ta có: $2^{2x^2-7x+5} = 1 \\Leftrightarrow 2x^2-7x+5 = 0 \\Leftrightarrow \\begin{cases} x = 1 \\\\ x = \\frac{5}{2} \\end{cases}$"
